{
  "stem": "10010.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And another thing-- my grandfather, every morning, he told me, oh, good morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jump from bed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We'll say now the prayer, which was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he taught me to pray.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And why do I mention it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because during the war, when I was on the Aryan side with the Poles, I-- I had to-- I-- I was under assumed-- different name.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I had to act as a Polish girl, as a non-Jewish girl, as a Christian one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But every morning, I stood before the window and I said, [NON-ENGLISH] in Hebrew, so nobody will hear-- only me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said this they cannot take away from me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and besides, I remember this time as very lovely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandmother, she was wearing a wig-- wig, naturally.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she-- oh-- Friday night, she was making the challahs and cookies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she gave me the cookies with milk every morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I loved them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then when she prepared everything, I helped her to do a little challah.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We brought it in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There used to be a cellar, because there were not Frigidaires in this time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So she put everything in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my grandfather made wine from raisins, like for Friday night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then on Friday night, we brought everything up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had the fish, the gefilte fish, like real gefilte fish, with the gefilte things in the fish itself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I have lovely, lovely memories from this time from my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's why I wanted to mention.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And also, my parents-- my father was very respectful to his family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Very often-- ah-- I have to come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
